579
00:43:21,040 --> 00:43:26,120
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

580
00:43:27,890 --> 00:43:33,240
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

581
00:43:33,550 --> 00:43:39,040
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

582
00:43:41,630 --> 00:43:46,650
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

583
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:53,680
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

584
00:43:55,280 --> 00:44:00,700
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

585
00:44:01,160 --> 00:44:06,660
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

586
00:44:07,860 --> 00:44:11,820
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

587
00:44:11,820 --> 00:44:16,810
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

588
00:44:16,940 --> 00:44:20,370
♪And full of life♪

589
00:44:21,660 --> 00:44:25,120
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

590
00:44:25,120 --> 00:44:30,230
